# unpact

A lightweight library for tabulating dictionaries.

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="99" height="20">
    <linearGradient id="b" x2="0" y2="100%">
